---
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Full-Stack Custom Systems | Intelio - AI-Powered Business Infrastructure" description="Purpose-built software from database to interface. Custom systems you own, we maintain. Built for competitive advantage, not off-the-shelf compromise.">
<main class="bg-white">
  <!-- HERO SECTION -->
  <section class="hero-section relative h-[700px] md:h-[700px] flex items-center overflow-hidden pt-20 md:pt-24">
    <!-- Animated Gradient Background -->
    <div class="hero-gradient absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-gray-900 via-blue-900 to-gray-900"></div>
    
    <!-- Subtle Data Visualization Background -->
    <div class="hero-visual absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
      <svg class="w-full h-full" viewBox="0 0 1200 800" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
        <!-- Connected Nodes Pattern -->
        <circle cx="200" cy="150" r="4" fill="#3b82f6" opacity="0.6"/>
        <circle cx="400" cy="200" r="4" fill="#3b82f6" opacity="0.6"/>
        <circle cx="600" cy="180" r="4" fill="#3b82f6" opacity="0.6"/>
        <circle cx="800" cy="220" r="4" fill="#3b82f6" opacity="0.6"/>
        <circle cx="1000" cy="160" r="4" fill="#3b82f6" opacity="0.6"/>
        <line x1="200" y1="150" x2="400" y2="200" stroke="#3b82f6" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.3"/>
        <line x1="400" y1="200" x2="600" y2="180" stroke="#3b82f6" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.3"/>
        <line x1="600" y1="180" x2="800" y2="220" stroke="#3b82f6" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.3"/>
        <line x1="800" y1="220" x2="1000" y2="160" stroke="#3b82f6" stroke-width="1" opacity="0.3"/>
        <!-- Database Cylinders -->
        <rect x="150" y="400" width="60" height="120" rx="4" fill="#3b82f6" opacity="0.15"/>
        <rect x="300" y="380" width="60" height="140" rx="4" fill="#3b82f6" opacity="0.15"/>
        <rect x="450" y="420" width="60" height="100" rx="4" fill="#3b82f6" opacity="0.15"/>
      </svg>
    </div>
    
    <!-- Glassmorphism Card Container -->
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-10 py-20 md:py-24 w-full relative z-10">
      <div class="hero-content max-w-3xl backdrop-blur-sm bg-white/5 rounded-2xl border border-white/10 p-8 md:p-12 shadow-2xl">
        <!-- Headline with Gradient Text -->
        <h1 class="hero-headline text-5xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white leading-[1.2] mb-6 tracking-tight hero-fade-in">
          <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-white via-blue-100 to-white bg-clip-text text-transparent">Full-Stack Custom Systems</span>
          <div class="hero-underline w-32 h-1 bg-blue-600 mt-4 rounded-full"></div>
        </h1>
        
        <!-- Subheading -->
        <p class="hero-subheading text-2xl md:text-3xl text-gray-200 mb-8 leading-relaxed font-semibold hero-fade-in-delay-1">
          The software that actually runs your business.
        </p>
        
        <!-- Description -->
        <p class="hero-description text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-300 mb-10 leading-relaxed hero-fade-in-delay-2">
          Off-the-shelf tools are built for everyone. That means they're built for no one.<br><br>
          Your workflows are unique. Your data is unique. Your competitive edge depends on systems that fit exactly how you operate—not systems that force you to operate like everyone else.<br><br>
          We engineer full-stack systems from database to interface. Complete ownership. Complete control. Complete leverage.
        </p>
        
        <!-- CTA Buttons -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 hero-buttons hero-fade-in-delay-3">
          <a href="#what-we-build" class="hero-primary-btn inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-500 text-white text-base font-semibold rounded-lg transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg hover:shadow-blue-500/50 hover:scale-105 group">
            Explore Full-Stack Systems
            <svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform duration-300" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7" />
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="/contact" class="hero-secondary-btn inline-flex items-center px-8 py-4 border-2 border-white/30 hover:border-white/60 text-white text-base font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm transition-all duration-300">
            Schedule Discovery
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CREDIBILITY BAR -->
  <section class="py-12 px-6 bg-white border-b border-gray-100">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-6">
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 font-medium">Trusted by operations leaders at:</p>
        <!-- Client Logos - Infinite Scroll -->
        <div class="logo-marquee-container w-full">
          <div class="logo-marquee-track">
            <!-- First set of logos -->
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/Newmark-logo.png" alt="Newmark" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium" style="display:none;">Newmark</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/hhp-grey-logo.png" alt="HHP" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium" style="display:none;">HHP</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/alliance-resource.png" alt="Alliance Resource Partners" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium text-sm" style="display:none;">Alliance Resource Partners</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/manhattan-construction-logo.png" alt="Manhattan Construction" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium text-sm" style="display:none;">Manhattan Construction</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/brain-body-soul-logo.png" alt="Brain Body Soul" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium text-sm" style="display:none;">Brain Body Soul</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/JLL-Logo.png" alt="JLL" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium" style="display:none;">JLL</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/CB logo.png" alt="CB" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium" style="display:none;">CB</span>
            </div>
            <!-- Duplicate set for seamless loop -->
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/Newmark-logo.png" alt="Newmark" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium" style="display:none;">Newmark</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/hhp-grey-logo.png" alt="HHP" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium" style="display:none;">HHP</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/alliance-resource.png" alt="Alliance Resource Partners" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium text-sm" style="display:none;">Alliance Resource Partners</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/manhattan-construction-logo.png" alt="Manhattan Construction" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium text-sm" style="display:none;">Manhattan Construction</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/brain-body-soul-logo.png" alt="Brain Body Soul" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium text-sm" style="display:none;">Brain Body Soul</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/JLL-Logo.png" alt="JLL" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium" style="display:none;">JLL</span>
            </div>
            <div class="logo-marquee-item">
              <img src="/logos/CB logo.png" alt="CB" class="logo-marquee-img" onerror="this.style.display='none'; this.nextElementSibling.style.display='block';">
              <span class="text-gray-400 font-medium" style="display:none;">CB</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- PROBLEM SECTION -->
  <section class="problem-section py-20 md:py-24 px-6 bg-white relative">
    <!-- Left Accent Line (Animated) -->
    <div class="problem-accent-line absolute left-0 top-0 w-1 bg-blue-600 rounded-full z-10"></div>
    
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto relative z-10">
      <div class="mb-16 scroll-fade-in">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6 inline-block pb-4 border-b-4 border-blue-600">
          Why Your Current Approach Is Costing You
        </h2>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-600 max-w-3xl leading-relaxed mt-6 mb-12">
          You're probably running on some combination of spreadsheets, disconnected tools, and institutional knowledge living in people's heads. It feels normal because every business does it. That doesn't make it less destructive.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="space-y-10 relative pl-8">
        <!-- Problem 1 -->
        <div class="problem-card bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-blue-50/30 rounded-lg p-8 border-t-4 border-l-4 border-blue-600 border-r border-b border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 scroll-fade-in">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="problem-icon flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7h12m0 0l-4-4m4 4l-4 4m0 6H4m0 0l4 4m-4-4l4-4"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-3">Fragmented Tools Create Fragmented Reality</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                Three different systems. Three different versions of truth. Teams make decisions on incomplete information because the complete picture doesn't exist anywhere.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Problem 2 -->
        <div class="problem-card bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-blue-50/30 rounded-lg p-8 border-t-4 border-l-4 border-blue-600 border-r border-b border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 scroll-fade-in">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="problem-icon flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6V4m0 2a2 2 0 100 4m0-4a2 2 0 110 4m-6 8a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4m6 6v10m6-2a2 2 0 100-4m0 4a2 2 0 110-4m0 4v2m0-6V4"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-3">Manual Processes Don't Scale</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                Works with 5 people. Breaks with 50. Growth adds administrative burden, not capability. Your team manages spreadsheets instead of building.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Problem 3 -->
        <div class="problem-card bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-blue-50/30 rounded-lg p-8 border-t-4 border-l-4 border-blue-600 border-r border-b border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 scroll-fade-in">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="problem-icon flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18.364 18.364A9 9 0 005.636 5.636m12.728 12.728A9 9 0 015.636 5.636m12.728 12.728L5.636 5.636"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-3">Low-Code Tools Hit a Wall</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                Great for simple problems. The moment requirements get sophisticated, you hit the platform's ceiling. Premium prices for tools that can't do what you need.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Problem 4 -->
        <div class="problem-card bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-blue-50/30 rounded-lg p-8 border-t-4 border-l-4 border-blue-600 border-r border-b border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 scroll-fade-in">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="problem-icon flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-3">You Don't Own Your System</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                You're renting the vendor's product. At the mercy of their roadmap. Constrained by their platform. Your competitive advantage belongs to them.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Problem 5 -->
        <div class="problem-card bg-gradient-to-br from-white to-blue-50/30 rounded-lg p-8 border-t-4 border-l-4 border-blue-600 border-r border-b border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 scroll-fade-in">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="problem-icon flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 7h8m0 0v8m0-8l-8 8-4-4-6 6"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-3">Growth Becomes Friction</h3>
              <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                Every new market or product line means rebuilding. You're compounding complexity, not accelerating. Systems that powered $1M can't power $10M.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- WHAT WE BUILD SECTION -->
  <section id="what-we-build" class="py-20 md:py-24 px-6 bg-gray-50">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">
          Purpose-Built Systems. Your Competitive Advantage.
        </h2>
        <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-blue-600 mx-auto mb-6"></div>
        <p class="text-base text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
          We don't configure templates or connect tools. We engineer complete systems from the database layer to the user interface. Every component is designed around how your business actually operates. Every decision is made for your advantage, not the vendor's roadmap.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <!-- Card 1: Database Architecture -->
        <div class="capability-card bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-50 rounded-xl p-10 border-t-2 border-blue-600 border-r border-b border-l border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 scroll-fade-in-stagger" style="animation-delay: 0ms;">
          <div class="relative mb-6">
            <div class="capability-badge absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold">01</div>
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-100 to-blue-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-md hover:rotate-6 transition-transform duration-300">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 7v10c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4V7M4 7c0 2.21 3.582 4 8 4s8-1.79 8-4M4 7c0-2.21 3.582-4 8-4s8 1.79 8 4m0 5c0 2.21-3.582 4-8 4s-8-1.79-8-4"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="h-0.5 w-12 bg-gray-200 mb-4"></div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-3">Database Architecture That Thinks Like Your Business</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Relational databases that capture your business logic. Deal matrices. Project tracking. Financial forecasting. A single source of truth—not a workaround.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 2: Intelligent Automation -->
        <div class="capability-card bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-50 rounded-xl p-10 border-t-2 border-blue-600 border-r border-b border-l border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 scroll-fade-in-stagger" style="animation-delay: 100ms;">
          <div class="relative mb-6">
            <div class="capability-badge absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold">02</div>
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-100 to-blue-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-md hover:rotate-6 transition-transform duration-300">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="h-0.5 w-12 bg-gray-200 mb-4"></div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-3">Automation That Responds to Business Reality</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Workflows triggered by database changes. Business events routed automatically. Data synced without manual intervention. Transparent, versionable, business-logic-driven.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 3: Custom Interfaces -->
        <div class="capability-card bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-50 rounded-xl p-10 border-t-2 border-blue-600 border-r border-b border-l border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 scroll-fade-in-stagger" style="animation-delay: 200ms;">
          <div class="relative mb-6">
            <div class="capability-badge absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold">03</div>
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-100 to-blue-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-md hover:rotate-6 transition-transform duration-300">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 17V7m0 10a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2V7a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m0 10a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 7a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m0 10V7m0 10a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2a2 2 0 00-2 2"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="h-0.5 w-12 bg-gray-200 mb-4"></div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-3">Interfaces Designed for How Your Team Works</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            Custom React interfaces built from scratch. Real-time dashboards. Forms that guide decisions. Reports that answer the questions leadership asks. The software adapts to your team.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 4: Seamless Integration -->
        <div class="capability-card bg-gradient-to-b from-white to-gray-50 rounded-xl p-10 border-t-2 border-blue-600 border-r border-b border-l border-gray-200 hover:border-blue-500 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 scroll-fade-in-stagger" style="animation-delay: 300ms;">
          <div class="relative mb-6">
            <div class="capability-badge absolute -top-2 -right-2 w-8 h-8 bg-blue-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-bold">04</div>
            <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-100 to-blue-50 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center shadow-md hover:rotate-6 transition-transform duration-300">
              <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M11 4a2 2 0 114 0v1a1 1 0 001 1h3a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-1a2 2 0 100 4h1a1 1 0 011 1v3a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3a1 1 0 01-1-1v-1a2 2 0 10-4 0v1a1 1 0 01-1 1H7a1 1 0 01-1-1v-3a1 1 0 00-1-1H4a2 2 0 110-4h1a1 1 0 001-1V7a1 1 0 011-1h3a1 1 0 001-1V4z"/>
              </svg>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="h-0.5 w-12 bg-gray-200 mb-4"></div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-blue-600 mb-3">Your Existing Tools, Now Connected</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            We integrate with what you have—CRM, accounting, scheduling. Your custom system connects all the pieces. Data flows automatically. One source of truth.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Card 5: Infrastructure -->
